  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Defeat droves of dive-bombing penguins! Squash squadrons of flying pigs! Trash tons of turbo-powered sheep! It's all waiting for you in this wacky, whirlwind adventure through the Amazatorium.\n\nFIVE wild worlds.\nFOUR claw-biting levels of difficulty.\nTHREE mind-boggling mini-games.\nTWO hopelessly lost relatives.\nand ONE wise-cracking bobcat named Bubsy.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The antagonist, Oinker P. Hamm, has created his \"Amazatorium\", which actually saps information away from history, and puts it on display, for his personal profit. It's up to the player to control Bubsy and stop this.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
